<OptimizedImage src="/assets/La-nueva-violencia-moderna-portada-1016x1536.webp" alt="La Nueva Violencia Moderna - Portada del libro" class="w-56 sm:w-64 md:w-72 h-auto rounded shadow-lg group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
</div>
